    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Faerain is an action survival  game, where the player tests their ability to survive large waves of enemies while gaining unique abilities and power-ups that can be used to their advantage. Enchanted rain falls from the cosmos corrupting anything that it touches, be the last to survive within the time limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Unique Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Playable Characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Combat Types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Progression ( Skill Tree, Upgrades, Items )</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight unique enemies and empower your character with various skills in order to survive against the corruption.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/5c15764d7c12d32aa46232cebe2958c1.poster.avif?t=1734708399\" width=574 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/5c15764d7c12d32aa46232cebe2958c1.webm?t=1734708399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/5c15764d7c12d32aa46232cebe2958c1.mp4?t=1734708399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover and upgrade equipment found throughout the world. Learn improved skills and unlock unique appearances.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/d6c65472019b32cd8d3ae34a5dcc9d17.poster.avif?t=1734708399\" width=726 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/d6c65472019b32cd8d3ae34a5dcc9d17.webm?t=1734708399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/d6c65472019b32cd8d3ae34a5dcc9d17.mp4?t=1734708399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore unique areas with different enemies and look.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/d42b6d8fa2574d317168ef5992d5445e.poster.avif?t=1734708399\" width=632 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/d42b6d8fa2574d317168ef5992d5445e.webm?t=1734708399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060440/extras/d42b6d8fa2574d317168ef5992d5445e.mp4?t=1734708399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
